beer.beer_description:
Created and brewed by the women of Bright Brewery, Fred's FOG IPA is a fresh and fruity IPA. Embrace the beautifully balanced orange, feijoa, and subtle guava flavours and aromas. 

Malts: Pale, Munich, Carahell, Oat, Wheat 
Hops: Centennial, Galaxy
Yeast: NE-E 
Other: Feijoa powder, blood orange & guava 
Colour: Orange
